snippet.title: Ryan Kinel - RK Outpost
snippet.description:
Welcome to my channel, RK Outpost!

Want to send me something?  That's amazing!:

Ryan Kinel - RK Outpost
PO Box 28
Tavares, FL 32778

I'm Ryan Kinel. I've a 11 year veteran of the United States Navy, and I'm passionate about nearly everything in my life, including entertainment, sports, gaming and politics.

On this channel, you'll find honest opinions and straight talk.  Leave a comment and join the discussion!

If you'd like to support my channel, check out my Patreon!
https://www.patreon.com/rkoutpost

Support the channel through my TeePublic Store!
